       <article class="template-content" id="main-col"> 
        <div class="row"> 
         <!-- hasSidebar --> 
         <div class="twelve columns content-col templatecontent"> 
          <section id="main-col-full"> 
           <div class="pagename-wrap"> 
            <div class="row"> 
             <div class="twelve columns"> 
              <h2 class="pagename">Departments, Majors &amp; Minors</h2> 
             </div>
             <!-- columns --> 
            </div>
            <!-- row --> 
            <!-- hasSocialIcons --> 
           </div>
           <!-- pagename-wrap --> 
           <!-- TitleNeeded --> 
           <!-- CalEvent --> 
           <h2><img class="right" src="assets/Uploads/_resampled/ResizedImage350233-Choices2.png" alt="" title="" width="350" height="233">Choices, choices.</h2> 
           <p>With more than 80 majors and academic programs, six preprofessional options, and two five-year combined master's programs, you can design a course of study that meets your career goals. Whatever you choose, you can't go wrong: All four of the university's academic colleges have received the highest ranking from the top accreditation boards in the fields.</p> 
           <h2>List of Departments, Majors &amp; Minors</h2> 
           <ul>
            <li><a href="programs-a-z-listings/">A-Z Listings</a></li> 
            <li><a href="programs-by-college/">By College </a></li> 
           </ul>
           <h2>Undecided?</h2> 
           <p>Our innovative <a href="aep/">Academic Exploration Program</a> welcomes students like you who are still investigating the subjects and careers that interest them. We're here to help you narrow the field and take the right courses to put you on the path to a good decision.</p> 
          </section>
